SQL: SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey", COUNT(*) as agg_0, avg("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_1, max("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_2 FROM "supplier"  WHERE "supplier"."s_address" != 'NZdeHwqAU' GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_suppkey";

SELECT max("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1, sum("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_2 FROM "supplier"  WHERE "supplier"."s_nation" IN ('SAUDI ARABIA', 'ETHIOPIA', 'UNITED STATES', 'JORDAN', 'MOROCCO') AND (CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%PERU%' OR (CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%R%OMANIA%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%B%RAZIL%')) AND "supplier"."s_nation" = 'MOROCCO';

SELECT "part"."p_size", "part"."p_mfgr", max("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1, avg("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_2 FROM "part"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_name" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%frost%ed%' AND ("part"."p_container" IN ('SM BOX', 'LG BOX', 'JUMBO JAR', 'LG CAN', 'WRAP BOX', 'WRAP CAN', 'WRAP JAR', 'LG JAR', 'MED PACK', 'WRAP CASE', 'MED JAR', 'MED BAG', 'MED PKG', 'SM CAN', 'MED DRUM', 'WRAP DRUM', 'MED BOX', 'JUMBO BOX', 'SM PACK', 'WRAP PKG', 'MED CASE', 'WRAP PACK', 'SM DRUM', 'JUMBO PKG', 'SM JAR', 'SM CASE', 'JUMBO CASE', 'JUMBO BAG', 'JUMBO DRUM', 'SM PKG', 'JUMBO PACK', 'LG PACK', 'LG PKG', 'WRAP BAG', 'LG CASE', 'JUMBO CAN', 'LG BAG') OR CAST("part"."p_container" AS varchar) LIKE '%DRUM%' OR "part"."p_container" != 'MED CASE') AND CAST("part"."p_color" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%mint%' AND "part"."p_type" != 'PROMO BRUSHED NICKEL' GROUP BY "part"."p_size", "part"."p_mfgr" ORDER BY "part"."p_size", "part"."p_mfgr";
SELECT max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "customer";

SELECT "supplier"."s_nation", sum("lineorder"."lo_discount" + "lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1, sum("lineorder"."lo_revenue") as agg_2 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "part" ON "lineorder"."lo_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"  WHERE "part"."p_type" = 'LARGE BRUSHED BRASS' AND "lineorder"."lo_partkey" BETWEEN 56749 AND 57740 AND CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%C%ANADA%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%AFRICA%' AND "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" >= 1 GROUP BY "supplier"."s_nation" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_nation";

SELECT "customer"."c_city", min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%FURNITURE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%BUILDING%' AND "customer"."c_nation" IN ('ALGERIA', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'UNITED KINGDOM', 'VIETNAM', 'KENYA', 'GERMANY', 'ARGENTINA', 'UNITED STATES', 'INDIA', 'BRAZIL', 'MOROCCO', 'ETHIOPIA', 'JORDAN', 'PERU', 'JAPAN', 'FRANCE', 'CHINA') AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%GERMAN%Y%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_city" ORDER BY "customer"."c_city";
SELECT sum("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0 FROM "supplier"  WHERE "supplier"."s_nation" != 'IRAN';

SELECT min("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_0, avg("part"."p_partkey") as agg_1 FROM "part"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_category" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MFGR#%42%' AND "part"."p_container" != 'SM PKG' AND (CAST("part"."p_mfgr" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MFGR#5%' OR "part"."p_brand1" = 'MFGR#1133' OR "part"."p_mfgr" IN ('MFGR#1', 'MFGR#5', 'MFGR#3')) AND "part"."p_name" = 'purple dodger';

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_suppkey", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", avg("lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_commitdate") as agg_1, min("lineorder"."lo_tax" + "lineorder"."lo_orderkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" != '4-NOT SPECIFIED' AND "customer"."c_custkey" BETWEEN 9825 AND 19445 AND (CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%5-LOW%' OR "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" = 5) AND ("lineorder"."lo_discount" >= 2 OR ("lineorder"."lo_partkey" >= 161216 AND "lineorder"."lo_discount" >= 8)) AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MOR%OCCO%' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_suppkey", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_suppkey", "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority";

SELECT "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_mktsegment", min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, sum("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1 FROM "customer"  WHERE "customer"."c_mktsegment" = 'FURNITURE' GROUP BY "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_mktsegment" ORDER BY "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_mktsegment";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", "supplier"."s_name", COUNT(*) as agg_0, sum("lineorder"."lo_revenue" + "lineorder"."lo_orderdate") as agg_1 FROM "supplier" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineorder"."lo_suppkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" != '1-URGENT' AND "lineorder"."lo_shippriority" != 0 AND "lineorder"."lo_discount" >= 3 GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", "supplier"."s_name" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", "supplier"."s_name";

SELECT "supplier"."s_region", "supplier"."s_name", max("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0 FROM "supplier"  WHERE "supplier"."s_region" IN ('EUROPE', 'MIDDLE EAST') AND CAST("supplier"."s_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%CHINA%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AL%GERIA%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%GE%RMANY%' GROUP BY "supplier"."s_region", "supplier"."s_name" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_region", "supplier"."s_name";

SELECT "supplier"."s_nation", avg("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0 FROM "supplier"  WHERE "supplier"."s_region" IN ('ASIA', 'AMERICA', 'EUROPE') OR "supplier"."s_nation" IN ('INDONESIA', 'GERMANY', 'UNITED STATES', 'INDIA', 'KENYA', 'IRAN', 'ETHIOPIA', 'ALGERIA', 'ARGENTINA', 'EGYPT', 'RUSSIA', 'CANADA', 'VIETNAM', 'UNITED KINGDOM', 'JAPAN', 'JORDAN', 'FRANCE') OR CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%M%IDDLE%' GROUP BY "supplier"."s_nation" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_nation";

SELECT avg("lineorder"."lo_extendedprice" + "lineorder"."lo_tax") as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_partkey") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_tax" >= 2 AND CAST("part"."p_type" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%PLAT%ED%' AND "part"."p_partkey" BETWEEN 308364 AND 367336;

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "customer"  WHERE "customer"."c_nation" = 'GERMANY' AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('MACHINERY', 'HOUSEHOLD', 'BUILDING', 'FURNITURE') AND "customer"."c_city" = 'RUSSIA   7';

SELECT "part"."p_mfgr", "part"."p_category", COUNT(*) as agg_0, min("part"."p_size") as agg_1, min("part"."p_partkey") as agg_2 FROM "part"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_category" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MFGR#33%' GROUP BY "part"."p_mfgr", "part"."p_category" ORDER BY "part"."p_mfgr", "part"."p_category";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_quantity", sum("lineorder"."lo_extendedprice") as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_tax" + "lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_1, max("customer"."c_custkey" + "lineorder"."lo_revenue") as agg_2 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_custkey" >= 53316 AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%AIR%' AND "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" IN ('SHIP', 'TRUCK', 'REG AIR', 'AIR', 'MAIL', 'RAIL') AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%C%ANADA%' AND "customer"."c_region" IN ('EUROPE') GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_quantity" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_quantity";

SELECT avg("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0 FROM "customer"  WHERE (CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%GERMANY%' OR ("customer"."c_custkey" <= 38952 AND "customer"."c_city" != 'RUSSIA   4')) AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%RU%SSIA%' AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('BUILDING', 'HOUSEHOLD', 'FURNITURE', 'AUTOMOBILE') AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MIDDLE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%AMERICA%';

SELECT "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_region", min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%FURNIT%URE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%VIETNAM%' AND "customer"."c_custkey" <= 39572 AND (CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%STA%TES%' OR ("customer"."c_nation" IN ('INDIA') AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%A%RABIA%')) AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AFRICA%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_region" ORDER BY "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_region";
SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "part"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_type" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%ANODIZED%';

SELECT "part"."p_mfgr", "part"."p_size", avg("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_0, min("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_1 FROM "part"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_container" AS varchar) LIKE '%BOX%' AND "part"."p_partkey" <= 321466 AND CAST("part"."p_type" AS varchar) LIKE '%BRUSH%ED%' AND "part"."p_category" IN ('MFGR#21', 'MFGR#35', 'MFGR#43', 'MFGR#42', 'MFGR#33', 'MFGR#15', 'MFGR#14', 'MFGR#31', 'MFGR#24', 'MFGR#12', 'MFGR#22', 'MFGR#53', 'MFGR#32', 'MFGR#13', 'MFGR#25', 'MFGR#11', 'MFGR#51', 'MFGR#54', 'MFGR#45', 'MFGR#23') AND (CAST("part"."p_category" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MF%GR#12%' OR "part"."p_color" = 'forest') GROUP BY "part"."p_mfgr", "part"."p_size" ORDER BY "part"."p_mfgr", "part"."p_size";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_quantity", min("lineorder"."lo_quantity" + "lineorder"."lo_custkey") as agg_0 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "part" ON "lineorder"."lo_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "part"."p_partkey" <= 120079 AND ("customer"."c_nation" = 'CANADA' OR (CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%IRAN%' AND "customer"."c_nation" IN ('GERMANY', 'MOROCCO', 'UNITED STATES', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'BRAZIL', 'JORDAN', 'IRAN', 'MOZAMBIQUE', 'KENYA'))) AND ("customer"."c_mktsegment" != 'HOUSEHOLD' OR ("customer"."c_custkey" >= 612 AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('MACHINERY', 'FURNITURE'))) GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_quantity" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_quantity";

SELECT avg("lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_linenumber") as agg_1 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_orderdate" BETWEEN 19934380 AND 19941548 AND "lineorder"."lo_tax" BETWEEN 0 AND 7 AND "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" >= 1662;

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", min("customer"."c_custkey" + "lineorder"."lo_revenue") as agg_0 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE "customer"."c_nation" IN ('CANADA', 'ALGERIA', 'INDONESIA', 'ETHIOPIA', 'INDIA', 'JORDAN', 'IRAN', 'UNITED KINGDOM', 'MOROCCO', 'PERU', 'SAUDI ARABIA') AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) LIKE '%S%PECIFIED%' AND "lineorder"."lo_commitdate" <= 19972503 AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) LIKE '%FR%ANCE%' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_orderdate" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_orderdate";

SELECT "part"."p_category", "part"."p_container", COUNT(*) as agg_0 FROM "part"  WHERE "part"."p_type" IN ('SMALL BURNISHED NICKEL', 'PROMO PLATED COPPER', 'SMALL BRUSHED TIN', 'LARGE PLATED STEEL', 'STANDARD BURNISHED NICKEL', 'SMALL POLISHED NICKEL', 'SMALL BURNISHED TIN', 'PROMO BRUSHED STEEL', 'ECONOMY ANODIZED BRASS', 'ECONOMY POLISHED STEEL', 'MEDIUM BURNISHED NICKEL', 'SMALL ANODIZED NICKEL', 'STANDARD BURNISHED COPPER', 'STANDARD ANODIZED STEEL', 'ECONOMY ANODIZED COPPER', 'SMALL ANODIZED COPPER', 'STANDARD PLATED BRASS', 'MEDIUM PLATED COPPER', 'LARGE BURNISHED STEEL', 'SMALL BURNISHED STEEL', 'LARGE PLATED COPPER', 'PROMO POLISHED TIN') GROUP BY "part"."p_category", "part"."p_container" ORDER BY "part"."p_category", "part"."p_container";

SELECT min("lineorder"."lo_partkey" + "lineorder"."lo_discount") as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_orderdate" + "lineorder"."lo_discount") as agg_1 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%ASIA%' AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" != 'AUTOMOBILE' AND "customer"."c_nation" IN ('ROMANIA') AND "lineorder"."lo_commitdate" >= 19932701;

SELECT "part"."p_category", max("part"."p_size") as agg_0, sum("part"."p_size") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "part"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_category" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MFGR#1%3%' AND CAST("part"."p_color" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%o%range%' GROUP BY "part"."p_category" ORDER BY "part"."p_category";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_quantity", "lineorder"."lo_linenumber", avg("lineorder"."lo_ordertotalprice") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1, min("lineorder"."lo_partkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%IRAN%' AND "customer"."c_region" = 'AMERICA' AND "supplier"."s_nation" = 'ALGERIA' AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MAIL%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%EUROPE%' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_quantity", "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_quantity", "lineorder"."lo_linenumber";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_suppkey", sum("lineorder"."lo_discount") as agg_0 FROM "lineorder" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"  WHERE (CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%EA%ST%' OR (CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%EUROPE%' AND CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%E%AST%')) AND "supplier"."s_phone" = '12-813-916-8297' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_suppkey";

SELECT "supplier"."s_address", "customer"."c_mktsegment", avg("part"."p_size") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1, avg("part"."p_size" + "lineorder"."lo_partkey") as agg_2 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "supplier" ON "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%HOUSEHOLD%' AND "customer"."c_nation" IN ('BRAZIL', 'MOROCCO', 'CANADA', 'UNITED STATES', 'IRAQ', 'JORDAN', 'FRANCE', 'EGYPT', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'ROMANIA', 'MOZAMBIQUE', 'VIETNAM', 'JAPAN', 'GERMANY', 'KENYA', 'RUSSIA', 'PERU', 'ETHIOPIA', 'INDIA', 'IRAN') AND ("lineorder"."lo_suppkey" BETWEEN 2668 AND 2993 OR ("lineorder"."lo_custkey" BETWEEN 12735 AND 20535 AND "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" <= 2429)) AND ("customer"."c_custkey" <= 42419 OR "customer"."c_region" IN ('EUROPE')) AND "lineorder"."lo_shipmode" IN ('AIR', 'FOB', 'RAIL', 'REG AIR', 'SHIP') GROUP BY "supplier"."s_address", "customer"."c_mktsegment" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_address", "customer"."c_mktsegment";

SELECT avg("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_0, max("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_1 FROM "part"  WHERE "part"."p_container" != 'SM CASE' AND CAST("part"."p_container" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%JUM%BO%';

SELECT "supplier"."s_address", sum("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0, max("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_1, max("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_2 FROM "supplier"  WHERE CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%EUROPE%' GROUP BY "supplier"."s_address" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_address";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", avg("lineorder"."lo_custkey") as agg_0 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "customer"."c_custkey" BETWEEN 1505 AND 13858 AND (CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%MAIL%' OR CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%TRUCK%') GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_orderdate" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_orderdate";

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_tax", "lineorder"."lo_linenumber", COUNT(*) as agg_0, avg("lineorder"."lo_shippriority" + "lineorder"."lo_commitdate") as agg_1, sum("lineorder"."lo_commitdate") as agg_2 FROM "lineorder"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" = '5-LOW' AND "lineorder"."lo_orderdate" >= 19955430 AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%SHIP%' AND "lineorder"."lo_shippriority" BETWEEN 0 AND 1 GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_tax", "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_tax", "lineorder"."lo_linenumber";

SELECT sum("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%MOROCCO%' AND (CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%SAUDI%' OR ("customer"."c_nation" = 'GERMANY' AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%EG%YPT%')) AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%FURNIT%URE%';

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_shippriority", "lineorder"."lo_commitdate", COUNT(*) as agg_0, max("lineorder"."lo_supplycost" + "customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, COUNT(*) as agg_2 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%TRU%CK%' AND "lineorder"."lo_orderdate" BETWEEN 19930878 AND 19971011 AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%M%ACHINERY%' GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_shippriority", "lineorder"."lo_commitdate" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_shippriority", "lineorder"."lo_commitdate";

SELECT sum("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_0, sum("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_1, max("part"."p_size" + "part"."p_partkey") as agg_2 FROM "part"  WHERE "part"."p_color" IN ('dodger', 'snow', 'sandy', 'thistle', 'tomato', 'lace', 'metallic', 'pale', 'rosy', 'spring', 'lavender', 'cyan', 'ivory') AND CAST("part"."p_category" AS varchar) LIKE '%MFG%R#51%';

SELECT "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate", avg("lineorder"."lo_shippriority") as agg_0 FROM "lineorder"  WHERE CAST("lineorder"."lo_orderpriority" AS varchar) LIKE '%3-MEDIUM%' AND "lineorder"."lo_commitdate" >= 19929709 AND "lineorder"."lo_orderkey" BETWEEN 634805 AND 2415495 AND CAST("lineorder"."lo_shipmode" AS varchar) LIKE '%FOB%' AND "lineorder"."lo_partkey" BETWEEN 77516 AND 83526 GROUP BY "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate" ORDER BY "lineorder"."lo_orderpriority", "lineorder"."lo_orderdate";

SELECT max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MIDDLE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%AMER%ICA%' AND ("customer"."c_mktsegment" = 'HOUSEHOLD' OR "customer"."c_nation" IN ('KENYA', 'MOZAMBIQUE', 'FRANCE', 'EGYPT', 'JORDAN', 'ETHIOPIA', 'BRAZIL', 'UNITED STATES', 'ARGENTINA', 'IRAQ', 'CHINA', 'ROMANIA', 'VIETNAM', 'IRAN', 'ALGERIA', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'GERMANY', 'MOROCCO') OR CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MAC%HINERY%');

SELECT max("lineorder"."lo_tax") as agg_0, COUNT(*) as agg_1 FROM "part" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineorder"."lo_partkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_tax" <= 2 AND "part"."p_partkey" >= 186846 AND "lineorder"."lo_partkey" <= 20074;

SELECT "customer"."c_mktsegment", COUNT(*) as agg_0, avg("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, sum("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%AUTOMOBILE%' AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) LIKE '%KINGDOM%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_mktsegment" ORDER BY "customer"."c_mktsegment";

SELECT "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_nation", min("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, avg("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer"  WHERE "customer"."c_region" IN ('AFRICA', 'EUROPE', 'AMERICA', 'MIDDLE EAST') AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" IN ('HOUSEHOLD', 'FURNITURE') GROUP BY "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_nation" ORDER BY "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_nation";

SELECT "customer"."c_region", sum("lineorder"."lo_orderkey" + "lineorder"."lo_partkey") as agg_0, min("lineorder"."lo_supplycost") as agg_1 FROM "supplier" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "lineorder"."lo_suppkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "part" ON "lineorder"."lo_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey" LEFT OUTER JOIN "customer" ON "lineorder"."lo_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"  WHERE "part"."p_size" <= 41 AND "part"."p_category" = 'MFGR#53' AND "customer"."c_region" = 'ASIA' AND "customer"."c_region" IN ('AMERICA', 'ASIA') AND "customer"."c_custkey" BETWEEN 56714 AND 56744 GROUP BY "customer"."c_region" ORDER BY "customer"."c_region";

SELECT COUNT(*) as agg_0, sum("lineorder"."lo_revenue") as agg_1 FROM "customer" LEFT OUTER JOIN "lineorder" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "lineorder"."lo_custkey"  WHERE "lineorder"."lo_supplycost" BETWEEN 54976 AND 93286 AND "lineorder"."lo_linenumber" BETWEEN 2 AND 6 AND "lineorder"."lo_custkey" <= 11589;

SELECT "supplier"."s_nation", "supplier"."s_name", min("supplier"."s_suppkey") as agg_0 FROM "supplier"  WHERE "supplier"."s_nation" IN ('INDIA', 'CHINA', 'GERMANY', 'MOZAMBIQUE', 'FRANCE', 'IRAN', 'BRAZIL', 'EGYPT', 'UNITED KINGDOM', 'JORDAN', 'IRAQ', 'PERU', 'JAPAN', 'VIETNAM', 'ARGENTINA', 'ETHIOPIA', 'ROMANIA', 'INDONESIA', 'MOROCCO', 'UNITED STATES', 'KENYA', 'SAUDI ARABIA', 'RUSSIA', 'ALGERIA') AND "supplier"."s_suppkey" BETWEEN 1986 AND 2644 AND CAST("supplier"."s_region" AS varchar) LIKE '%EURO%PE%' GROUP BY "supplier"."s_nation", "supplier"."s_name" ORDER BY "supplier"."s_nation", "supplier"."s_name";

SELECT sum("part"."p_partkey") as agg_0 FROM "part"  WHERE CAST("part"."p_category" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%MFGR#52%' AND ("part"."p_container" IN ('SM PKG', 'LG PKG', 'LG DRUM', 'SM CASE', 'WRAP DRUM', 'WRAP PKG', 'MED JAR', 'SM JAR', 'MED BAG', 'SM BOX', 'MED CAN', 'MED PKG', 'JUMBO CASE', 'JUMBO PACK', 'WRAP BAG', 'LG CAN', 'MED PACK', 'MED CASE', 'LG PACK') OR "part"."p_container" IN ('WRAP PACK', 'WRAP CAN', 'WRAP CASE', 'LG PKG', 'MED JAR', 'WRAP BOX', 'LG PACK', 'JUMBO CAN', 'SM CAN', 'SM PKG', 'LG CASE', 'SM DRUM', 'LG BAG', 'MED BOX', 'LG CAN', 'SM JAR', 'JUMBO BOX', 'MED PKG', 'MED CASE', 'JUMBO PKG', 'JUMBO PACK', 'JUMBO CASE', 'JUMBO DRUM', 'WRAP JAR', 'LG JAR', 'MED DRUM', 'JUMBO JAR', 'WRAP PKG', 'SM BAG', 'LG DRUM', 'SM BOX') OR "part"."p_container" != 'LG CASE') AND CAST("part"."p_color" AS varchar) LIKE '%cornflower%' AND "part"."p_mfgr" IN ('MFGR#2', 'MFGR#3', 'MFGR#1', 'MFGR#5');

SELECT "part"."p_type", min("part"."p_partkey" + "part"."p_size") as agg_0, avg("part"."p_size") as agg_1 FROM "part"  WHERE "part"."p_mfgr" IN ('MFGR#1') AND "part"."p_partkey" <= 164691 AND CAST("part"."p_name" AS varchar) LIKE '%honeydew%' GROUP BY "part"."p_type" ORDER BY "part"."p_type";

SELECT "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_city", max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1 FROM "customer"  WHERE CAST("customer"."c_region" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%EUROPE%' AND "customer"."c_custkey" >= 9682 AND CAST("customer"."c_nation" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%RUSS%IA%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_city" ORDER BY "customer"."c_mktsegment", "customer"."c_city";

SELECT "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_mktsegment", max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_0, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_1, max("customer"."c_custkey") as agg_2 FROM "customer"  WHERE "customer"."c_nation" = 'ARGENTINA' AND CAST("customer"."c_city" AS varchar) NOT LIKE '%SA%UDI%' AND CAST("customer"."c_mktsegment" AS varchar) LIKE '%AUTOMO%BILE%' GROUP BY "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_mktsegment" ORDER BY "customer"."c_city", "customer"."c_mktsegment";
